''
'' Retro Coast Theme - Transparent Palette
''
'' Makes the diagram canvas and element backgrounds transparent while
'' keeping all foreground colors, line colors, and C4 element colors
'' from the default Retro Coast theme.
''
'' Usage:
''   !include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chden/puml-themes/main/palettes/retro-coast-transparent.iuml
''   !theme retro-coast from https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chden/puml-themes/main/themes/retro-coast/
''
'' Author: Christoph Denninger
'' License: MIT
'' https://github.com/chden/puml-themes
''

!$BGCOLOR_ROOT ?= transparent
!$BGCOLOR ?= transparent
!$BOUNDARY_BGCOLOR ?= transparent
